WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:08.760
I saw that there's something coming, and it's revolving around the three I-Atlas.

00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:11.360
It's connected.

00:00:11.947 --> 00:00:14.880
Whatever this is is connected.

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:21.600
And the Lord said we're about to see something that's going to freak people out.

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:23.342
I saw the fire.

00:00:23.342 --> 00:00:31.860
I saw what he said was a shaking; it's going to be a call to wake up everybody.

00:00:31.860 --> 00:00:35.840
And what we're about to see in the heavens is a shaking in the heavens.

00:00:36.133 --> 00:00:41.760
He said it's going to be like blood; it's about fire and it's so loud.

00:00:42.750 --> 00:00:45.942
This is a major event that's about to take place.

00:00:45.942 --> 00:00:55.280
Something is coming, soon it's coming, and this is not an alien.

00:00:55.280 --> 00:01:00.719
There's no such thing as aliens; it's demonic spirits.

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:08.940
But what you're about to see is what Oral Roberts saw in 2004, called the 'Wake-up Call.

00:01:08.940 --> 00:01:21.947
' It will be a wake-up to the church, a wake-up to the world, a sign of the second coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:01:21.947 --> 00:01:32.400
It's time for preachers to preach fire back in the pulpits, to preach repentance back in the pulpits.

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:36.400
For there will be a sign in the heavens.

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:38.773
There will be a sign throughout the earth.

00:01:38.773 --> 00:01:44.136
Remember this word.

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:47.805
Timing was not right.

00:01:47.805 --> 00:01:55.413
You know, whenever you're seeing over in the spirit, it looks like it's right in front of your face, but there's something coming.

00:01:55.413 --> 00:02:01.733
And most of them know that it's coming—government—and it's not conspiracy.

00:02:03.497 --> 00:02:04.613
No, it's not conspiracy.

00:02:04.613 --> 00:02:06.728
That's what the Spirit of the Lord just said.

00:02:06.728 --> 00:02:12.549
He said this is not conspiracy; it's a sign of the second coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:02:12.549 --> 00:02:14.380
It's awakening up the world.

00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:41.680
Then I saw with my eyes something I'd never seen: suddenly in the clouds, in the skies above New York City and the east part of the United States, which hung there for quite some time and then spread out across America without touching the ground.

00:02:42.194 --> 00:02:50.879
Then God diffused it away from America and sent it out to the nations of the earth.

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:55.360
And I saw and I heard.

00:02:56.680 --> 00:03:06.151
I saw something coming down from above: smoke and vapor and blood.

00:03:06.151 --> 00:03:09.904
Or it looked like that to my spiritual eyes.

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:22.159
There it was hanging so huge until it almost blotted out the sky.

00:03:22.159 --> 00:03:30.147
Instantly I thought about 9/11 when the terrorists attacked the Twin Towers.

00:03:30.147 --> 00:03:40.600
First, I saw this thing hovering and great changes coming in it to where I couldn't miss it.

00:03:40.600 --> 00:03:59.200
And then I heard something come into my ears, and it reminded me of what a friend of mine had said when the first space capsule was released into the sky.

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:13.840
They told me that they made all of them—he was a newsman in New York City—be maybe half a mile or more away from the capsule.

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:25.973
And he said when that thing lifted off the earth, there was a sound, and the sound itself moved the weeds and the growth.

00:04:25.973 --> 00:04:30.187
And he said, 'It penetrated my body.

00:04:30.187 --> 00:04:34.299
' He said as I talked to others, they felt the same thing.

00:04:34.299 --> 00:04:42.880
He said the sound was so enormous that nothing had ever happened like it in the history of the world.

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:52.880
Instantly, I thought of that because the sound that was coming into my ears was penetrating my whole being.

00:04:52.880 --> 00:04:56.479
And then I heard God's voice.

00:04:56.479 --> 00:05:01.360
He said, 'I'm making a sign.

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:16.479
' This is a sign according to the second chapter of Acts where the Apostle Peter, upon the giving of the Holy Spirit, the baptism of the Holy Spirit, said there'll be signs in the skies.

00:05:16.769 --> 00:05:28.320
He said, 'This is one of the signs of the end time because the world is not ready for the second coming of my Son.

00:05:28.320 --> 00:05:34.560
' They are coming to church on Sunday morning mostly for themselves.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:45.600
And the preachers, for the most part, are not really concerned about the nations of the earth; they're concerned about the little group that is there.

00:05:45.1000 --> 00:05:49.863
They sing their songs and they get up and preach.

00:05:51.326 --> 00:06:09.919
When 9/11 struck, there was a fear that came into their hearts—even of my people of the church and of people outside the church—and millions the following Sunday rushed to go to church.

00:06:09.919 --> 00:06:10.628
That's right.

00:06:10.628 --> 00:06:28.000
But the preachers were not prepared, and most of them didn't even preach on it and didn't even talk about it being the sign of something that's coming hundreds of thousands of times bigger.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:44.120
He said when those planes of the terrorists struck the Twin Towers in New York City and they gradually came tumbling down, it was something bigger than people had ever seen.

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:53.600
But it's nothing in comparison to what's going to happen in the second coming of my Son.

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:58.903
And so he said, 'My church was not prepared to deal with that.

00:06:58.903 --> 00:07:07.610
' And people came to church and then nothing much happened, and they dropped back and many of them went back to their beds.

00:07:07.610 --> 00:07:11.805
There's a sign coming, a sign for the unbeliever.

00:07:13.173 --> 00:07:16.229
A sign for the unbeliever is coming.

00:07:19.680 --> 00:07:20.160
A sign.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:24.766
It's time to get on the boat.

00:07:24.766 --> 00:07:31.028
I've warned and warned and warned that within a 24-hour period, everything would change.

00:07:31.028 --> 00:07:36.046
Everything is going to change within a 24-hour period.

00:07:36.046 --> 00:07:41.222
The way you live life, everything is going to change.

00:07:41.222 --> 00:07:46.948
Where there'll be signs in the heavens, there'll be signs in the earth.

00:07:46.948 --> 00:07:55.943
There'll be signs in your politics, there'll be signs in your finances, and there'll be signs in your church.

00:07:55.943 --> 00:07:56.631
Sorrows.

00:07:56.631 --> 00:08:01.577
This is the beginning of sorrows—the labor pains upon a woman.

00:08:01.577 --> 00:08:03.759
So will it be.

00:08:03.759 --> 00:08:06.811
He's doing it out of mercy.

00:08:06.811 --> 00:08:11.699
He will do this out of love, and the church bells will ring.

00:08:11.699 --> 00:08:13.679
You'll see people—remember 9/11, how they all ran to church?

00:08:13.679 --> 00:08:19.620
It was the way, when Charlie Kirk died, they ran to church.

00:08:19.620 --> 00:08:26.880
But when you see these signs, they will run.

00:08:26.880 --> 00:08:29.759
But what will they get?

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:33.256
When these signs come, you must stay filled.

00:08:41.680 --> 00:08:42.120
You must stay filled for they're coming in hot.

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:44.628
You must stay filled, my harvesters.

00:08:44.628 --> 00:08:48.853
For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:08:48.853 --> 00:08:53.740
For you must stay filled for they're coming.

00:09:05.520 --> 00:09:05.920
Coming within a day from shore to shore.

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:07.413
They're coming in.

00:09:07.413 --> 00:09:08.799
Even the scoffers.

00:09:08.799 --> 00:09:10.212
I see Hollywood.

00:09:30.613 --> 00:09:30.987
I see deep blue states.

00:09:30.987 --> 00:09:32.853
I see the scoffers.

00:09:32.853 --> 00:09:42.903
Even in the red states, you'll see scoffers and mockers: 'Where is the coming of the Lord?

00:09:42.903 --> 00:09:48.183
' But this is his mercy and his grace.

00:09:48.183 --> 00:09:50.533
One last push, one last call.

00:09:52.293 --> 00:09:53.146
It's going to shake the world.

00:09:53.146 --> 00:09:54.852
He's going to make a sign.

00:09:54.852 --> 00:09:56.600
It's so loud in me.

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:58.280
I hear it so loud.

00:09:58.280 --> 00:10:01.880
There's a major event about to take place.

00:10:01.880 --> 00:10:05.580
Fearful sights you will see that will bring you to your knee.

00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:17.120
It's going to be a sign that the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ is at hand.

00:10:34.510 --> 00:10:34.780
The devils in hell know it.

00:10:34.780 --> 00:10:36.399
This is the theme tonight.

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:41.760
You need to understand what the Lord is trying to tell you.

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:43.200
Revelation 12...

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:46.279
read it one more time, love.

00:10:46.279 --> 00:10:46.880
Revelation 12:12.

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:50.951
Satan knows.

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:54.194
He knows.

00:10:54.194 --> 00:10:57.829
'Therefore, rejoice ye heavens, and ye that dwell in them.

00:10:57.829 --> 00:11:01.347
Woe to the inhabitors of the earth and of the sea!

00:11:01.347 --> 00:11:12.651
For the devil is come down unto you, having great wrath, because he knoweth that he hath but a short time.

00:11:12.651 --> 00:11:13.874
' It's coming to that time.

00:11:13.874 --> 00:11:15.1000
I know he's talking about tribulation.

00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:34.900
But he knows when we're getting close.

00:11:34.900 --> 00:11:37.817
He knows we have but a short time.

00:11:37.817 --> 00:11:44.347
Yes, he's coming in wrath, and this is tribulation that we're talking about.

00:11:44.347 --> 00:11:46.187
Well, 'Brandon, you're quoting tribulation.

00:11:46.187 --> 00:11:47.360
' I know.

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:51.240
But he knows when we're getting—there's something different.

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:51.840
Something's changing.

00:12:08.800 --> 00:12:09.120
And they know the pressure.

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:14.480
That's why I'm telling you, you're going to start to see things you never thought you would see.

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:18.132
The birthing and labor pains, they're increasing.

00:12:21.789 --> 00:12:22.569
And the Lord Jesus Christ is coming.

00:12:24.079 --> 00:12:26.754
And we're going to have a major harvest of souls.

00:12:26.754 --> 00:12:32.111
The glorious church without spot or wrinkle is rising up.

00:12:32.111 --> 00:12:37.200
But it's going to be a shaking to awaken.

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:40.880
I know people are talking about 2026, 2027, 2028.

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:42.430
I've seen into it.

00:12:42.430 --> 00:12:44.817
2029, 30, 31, all this time.

00:12:44.817 --> 00:12:50.560
I just know that we're not done with 2025 yet.

00:12:50.560 --> 00:12:54.813
We've got this little window of two months.

00:12:54.813 --> 00:12:56.686
There's still more to happen.

00:12:56.686 --> 00:12:59.519
How do we close out this year?

00:12:59.805 --> 00:13:00.948
What is the flash?

00:13:03.234 --> 00:13:03.577
What are these things I'm seeing?

00:13:03.577 --> 00:13:04.880
Acceleration of war.

00:13:04.880 --> 00:13:15.760
We're praying into it with Venezuela, and they say the drug cartels, the politics, and things are going on.

00:13:15.760 --> 00:13:17.839
We've got people hiding in bunkers.

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:27.060
What is happening?

00:13:27.060 --> 00:13:27.580
Why?

00:13:27.580 --> 00:13:28.620
What's going on?

00:13:28.620 --> 00:13:39.154
We must open our eyes and be more vigilant about what's happening and be watchmen and watchwomen looking at our horizon.

00:13:39.154 --> 00:13:40.639
There's much more there.

00:13:50.708 --> 00:13:51.085
We must pray for our president's protection.

00:13:51.085 --> 00:13:56.731
We must pray and intercede for his life.

00:13:56.731 --> 00:14:03.360
He must live long and finish strong and finish what God has called him to do.

00:14:03.360 --> 00:14:13.025
There's no one that's able to harm him with any kind of plan, plot, or pursuit, his health, all of it.

00:14:17.079 --> 00:14:17.412
With his kids, we must live long and finish strong.

00:14:18.666 --> 00:14:19.252
We're wrapping this thing up.

00:14:28.664 --> 00:14:28.912
The Lord said, "I'm giving you a three and a half year window.

00:14:28.912 --> 00:14:30.151
What will you do?

00:14:30.151 --> 00:14:32.959
" Now it's three years and two months.

00:14:32.959 --> 00:14:37.680
"What will you do with this time frame?

00:14:37.680 --> 00:14:41.462
" He said, "Will you go back into sleep?

00:14:41.462 --> 00:14:44.015
" Oh, church, what will you do?

00:14:44.015 --> 00:14:45.648
I've given you this time.

00:14:45.648 --> 00:14:49.199
And I said, "Most people look at the midterms as just a year away.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
" Well, it's a year away tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Midterms.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Now, what the Lord showed me was a stalemate government.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
I saw the losing of the Senate and keeping of the House, and the Lord said, "You're going to lose governors.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
You're going to lose if you don't pray now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
If you don't start interceding now, you'll lose the midterms.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
" You cannot wait until this time next year and say, "Well, we better pray.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
" I saw Oklahoma even being divided.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.500
I saw Texas with borders all around them, not wanting to secede from the United States, wanting to have their own country like we're not going to go this way.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Secede.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.800
I saw people very upset with Gavin, and I saw a red wave trying to come over California with people upset, saying, "Listen, we're taking back our state.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
" So, we must pray ahead of time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:22.750
I know we have a year and we'll pray into it a lot over the next year, but I have such an urgency to tell you we must keep even more of a majority in the Senate and in the House to pass forth legislation to get the job done that needs to be done so that we have all the things that we need.
